  "description": "## Deep Component Audit — hx-overflow-menu\n\n**Component directory:** `packages/hx-library/src/components/hx-overflow-menu/`\n\n### wc-mcp Tools — USE THESE\n- `score_component`, `get_component`, `analyze_accessibility`, `list_css_parts`, `list_events`, `list_slots`, `get_design_tokens`\n- **Report wc-mcp bugs to `/Volumes/Development/booked/wc-tools` board.**\n\n### Audit Scope\n1. **Design Tokens** — `--hx-` tokens. Trigger, menu panel, item hover. Dark mode.\n2. **Accessibility** — WCAG 2.1 AA. Menu button pattern. aria-expanded, aria-haspopup. Keyboard. Focus management on open/close.\n3. **Functionality** — Three-dot/kebab trigger. Menu items. Dividers. Disabled items. Positioning. Click-outside dismiss.\n4. **TypeScript** — Strict. No `any`.\n5. **CSS/Styling** — Shadow DOM. CSS Parts. Positioning. Z-index.\n6. **CEM Accuracy** — All API documented.\n7. **Tests** — 80%+ coverage. Toggle. Items. Keyboard. Positioning.\n8. **Storybook** — Default. With dividers. Disabled items. Positioning.\n9. **Drupal Compatibility** — Operations column. Twig-friendly.\n10. **Portability** — CDN-ready.\n\n### Deliverable\nDetailed audit report. Fix CRITICAL+HIGH. Document rest.",
